OL,3,CFormer Police Constable charged with
OL,4,C14 child sex offences
OL,6,FA former police officer has denied 14
OL,7,Fsexual offences relating to a teenager.
OL,9,FThomas Winstanley has pleaded guilty
OL,10,Fto all charges at Birmingham Crown
OL,11,FCourt, which are alleged to have taken
OL,12,Fplace while he was woking as a
OL,13,Fconstable for Lancashire Police.
OL,15,FHe was arrested in 2024 and suspended
OL,16,Ffrom duty, and has resigned from his
OL,17,Fposition.
OL,19,FBefore his resignation he worked as a
OL,20,Fresponse officer in South division,
OL,21,Fbased in Leyland.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
