OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1773414685
OL,3,CFormer Police Constable charged with
OL,4,C14 child sex offences
OL,6,FAt a hearing at Birmingham Crown Court
OL,7,Fin February, the former PC pleaded not
OL,8,Fguilty to three counts of rape of a
OL,9,Fgirl aged 13/14/15, sexual assault of
OL,10,Fa female, sexual activity with a girl
OL,11,Faged 13 to 15, causing or inciting a
OL,12,Fchild to engage in sexual activity,
OL,13,Fengaging in sexual communication with
OL,14,Fa child, engaging in sexual activity
OL,15,Fin the presence of a child and
OL,16,Fpossession of a prohibited image of a
OL,17,Fchild.
OL,19,FA trial date has been scheduled for 8
OL,20,FMay 2028.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
