CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1773414685
OL,3,CFormer Police Constable charged with
OL,4,C14 child sex offences
OL,6,FA Lancashire Police spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"We can confirm a Lancashire officer
OL,8,Fhas been charged with a number of
OL,9,Fsexual offences.
OL,11,F"Thomas Winstanley is a response PC
OL,12,Fwho was based in our South division.
OL,13,FHe was first arrested in October 2024
OL,14,Fand immediately suspended following
OL,15,Fhis arrest. The investigation has been
OL,16,Fmanaged independently by Cumbria
OL,17,FPolice.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
