OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1773414685
OL,3,CFormer Police Constable charged with
OL,4,C14 child sex offences
OL,6,F"Thomas Winstanley has tendered his
OL,7,Fresignation from Lancashire
OL,8,FConstabulary. Due to legal
OL,9,Fproceedings, we aren't able to offer
OL,10,Ffurther comment at this time."
